Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:05:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太  太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.66,0:05:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  我…我是…芥…芥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.47,0:05:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芥川丈途同學對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.39,0:05:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是園聲謠江  請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.24,0:05:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.76,0:05:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  天才高中生作家
#當然  天才高中生小說作家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.41,0:05:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  算是吧  但是那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您寫的是些什麼內容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.35,0:05:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這步還算不錯  目前為止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.99,0:05:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題就在這之後…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  變態
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.66,0:05:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我已經習以為常了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  想到要被她…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色情小說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.50,0:05:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別揭穿我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色…情?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.52,0:05:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.28,0:05:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著就捏啊煮啊踹啊各種各樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:05:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.20,0:05:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.44,0:06:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原本以為寫工口小說的都是些可怕的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.79,0:06:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  是工口哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這是在挑戰困難的類型沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被  被誇了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「描寫性也就是在描寫人」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在某個會談時教授有說過哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.20,0:06:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也這麼認為
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確  確實  沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也相信大家終有一天會理解我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.97,0:06:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼馬上進行採訪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教  園聲同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我謠江就可以了  丈途同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.41,0:06:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  謠江同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都是這麼認為
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.20,0:07:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為工口小說作家的我不可能有同齡的女性Fans
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.75,0:07:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這麼漂亮的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.54,0:07:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是學園頂級的天才偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.96,0:07:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然稱讚著我  稱讚著我的工口小說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.22,0:07:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提問就是這些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.19,0:07:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼接著是攝影取材
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.82,0:07:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.93,0:07:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  來夏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.39,0:07:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不幹了是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.89,0:07:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這不是你喜歡的那啥人性醜陋的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.06,0:07:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.47,0:07:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想拍冒牌貨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒牌貨?  園聲同學哪點像了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.86,0:08:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.87,0:08:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來夏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.07,0:08:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  來夏這麼自作主張
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.11,0:08:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然天才會明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.49,0:08:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡這份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱歌  跳舞都挺有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.64,0:08:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我也挺適合
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.16,0:08:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fan的各位也高興地為我加油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.44,0:08:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常感謝他們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.93,0:08:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  在心裡我一直在想著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.63,0:08:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是真正的我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.07,0:08:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.56,0:08:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Staff和Fan大家都稱讚我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.10,0:08:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都說我是一百分滿分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.29,0:08:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  這真的是我的全部嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.36,0:09:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想這只是憑借才能把工作做好而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.66,0:09:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謠江同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.99,0:09:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時我會覺得背叛了Fan的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令我無法忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.15,0:09:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是  你說昨天的取材還是不順利麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.98,0:09:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於學園第一的現役偶像真心的煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.72,0:09:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我這種平常的高中生也不能說什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.39,0:09:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.98,0:09:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是在全國擁有眾多Fans的天才作家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.95,0:09:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出自信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.85,0:09:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fans嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是世界數學會會場
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.07,0:09:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順帶一提  円修律的發表是關於
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.40,0:09:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金平糖突起物的發生概率與其角度的研究
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.41,0:09:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾  我發表的時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.15,0:09:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在巴塞隆納祝願你順利哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:10:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要什麼禮物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.80,0:10:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬥牛的模型  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.90,0:10:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡那種東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.47,0:10:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  劍士與牛相互衝突的那種…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互衝突?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互…衝突
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:16.09,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與「交往」同音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你總是這麼亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是同班同學  那  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律  冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.11,0:10:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慣例的那個魔咒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.88,0:10:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3.14…啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.89,0:10:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,159265…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律  我說了多餘的話  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也在日本的天空下為你祈禱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.68,0:10:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦  丈途同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.27,0:10:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取材進行得還順利麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.58,0:10:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那個  這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂堂七尺男兒  拋下柔弱女子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打退堂鼓此等事是不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.54,0:11:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  我絕對不會退縮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可期待著哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.37,0:11:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.55,0:11:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像那兩人所說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.56,0:11:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園聲同學可以說是我最難得的Fan不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.37,0:11:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能把這事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謠江同學請假了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.94,0:11:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在這裡  也不會過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.78,0:11:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.96,0:11:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謠江同學?  我不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.42,0:11:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.09,0:12:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有看到園聲同學嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.13,0:12:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.26,0:12:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找學校第一偶像有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.47,0:12:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可說在前頭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.79,0:12:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這樣的所有少女的公敵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.73,0:12:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼看都不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.35,0:12:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謠江同學是因為我的錯  才會這麼痛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.12,0:12:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須跟她談談  不能放著她不管
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.84,0:12:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我  蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.54,0:12:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.44,0:12:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  這麼認真
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.36,0:12:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.25,0:13:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.28,0:13:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人操心的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:36.98,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謠江  這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道是什麼回事  不過得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈途同學?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.58,0:13:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.15,0:13:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想事情的時候就會來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.33,0:13:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是秘密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.91,0:14:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吧  對世間的事情完全不瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得和班裡的同學相比
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全就是個小孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.53,0:14:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  才不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在從事大人工作的丈途同學看來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.03,0:14:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是很幼稚  無聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.06,0:14:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能妄想！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是妄想的時候！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.02,0:14:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便眼前果實纍纍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.84,0:14:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要強忍著咪咪的誘惑…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.84,0:14:38.30,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這句捏自「武士は食わねど高楊枝」  武士即使窮困也會以高姿態安於清貧  注重體面  也有故作忍耐之意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.30,0:14:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.20,0:14:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.45,0:14:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  臉好紅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.28,0:14:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是感冒了啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.57,0:15:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小說?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.55,0:15:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能聽我說嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是某個煩惱的歌姬與詩人的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌姬的苦惱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.72,0:15:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是千人讚賞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.43,0:15:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬人鼓掌  也不能使其滿足
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.43,0:15:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這前方  更前方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.79,0:15:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要跨越自身這道高牆的強烈願望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.62,0:15:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事只有詩人一個人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:16:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為詩人也做了無數次的嘗試
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以詩人開始唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.33,0:16:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了歌姬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.62,0:16:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是蛹之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.28,0:16:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛹?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是比世間所有的寶石都要美麗的蛹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.28,0:16:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有見過的人都想要讚美它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.89,0:16:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  在這深處隱藏著更為完美的事實
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.51,0:16:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翅膀正沉睡在你的體內
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝擊性的電流穿過歌姬的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.07,0:16:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算一直躲在這堅硬又狹小的蟲蛹之中嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.18,0:16:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你真正的願望嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.59,0:16:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.39,0:16:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩人的歌曲如蛛絲一般
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.63,0:16:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕獲了在硬殼下的歌姬的心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將其束縛  越纏越緊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.28,0:17:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩人繼續唱著歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.94,0:17:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要委身於自己真摯的心靈便可
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.18,0:17:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌聲已化為顎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.25,0:17:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用尖牙破壞掉包裹著歌姬的蛹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.88,0:17:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管什麼裝飾  對你來說都是不需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.59,0:17:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌姬好像被什麼操縱著似的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.39,0:17:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用發抖的手擺脫著蛹的束縛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在眼前的  已不再是詩人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.57,0:17:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰冷的目光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.58,0:17:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同火一般炙熱的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.85,0:17:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燥動不已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.53,0:17:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其存在本身化為一首歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.07,0:17:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷倒數百萬人的玉肌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.37,0:17:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯露於搖曳的光輝之中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:17:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.23,0:17:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:18:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  更加…更加…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.80,0:18:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.14,0:18:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩人的話語像是能將心靈融化一般
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化為充滿芳香的劇毒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深深滲透進歌姬的心裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.77,0:18:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔚藍的天空就在前方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌姬重獲新生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擺脫虛偽的蟲蛹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.60,0:18:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成了自由的蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.52,0:18:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛向了遙遠廣闊的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.45,0:18:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用她原有的姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用真實的姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.50,0:18:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛翔！ 飛起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛向新的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.23,0:18:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.52,0:18:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那既不是畏懼  也不是痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.88,0:19:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不是懊悔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.42,0:19:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是有生以來初次體驗到的幸福高潮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.40,0:19:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無可比擬的解放感
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌姬死去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.74,0:19:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  真正的歌姬在此誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.78,0:19:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  丈途同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.78,0:19:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.65,0:20:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這和之前完全不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啊  正是精彩的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.59,0:20:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後  發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.85,0:20:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼是指什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.54,0:20:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是再次取材而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.76,0:20:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.74,0:20:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.38,0:20:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢  總之好像是非常好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.43,0:20:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢  忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.03,0:20:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙腦子長在屁股上的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.70,0:20:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這可怕的色胚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.64,0:20:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈  可能是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.86,0:20:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞台煙火裝置  Ver.2
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.96,0:20:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.06,0:21:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我終於知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.02,0:21:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在舞台上的是真正的謠江同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.35,0:21:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人健壯的手將她的一切剝下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.41,0:21:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像剛出生一般無垢的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.09,0:21:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅被純粹的性慾纏繞著的胴體…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.65,0:21:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胴體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.14,0:21:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那並不僅是謠江同學的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.75,0:21:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.48,0:21:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲進名為借口的外殼  一個勁地逃避的我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.46,0:21:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要變成真正的我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.35,0:21:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我夢想中的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.12,0:21:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.24,0:22:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.14,0:22:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想對鳴唐同學…

